#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_sendfile.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Send a file to another user through a direct peer-to-peer connection. The file transfers directly between your browsers without going through the server."
msgstr "通过直接对等连接向另一个用户发送文件. 文件在浏览器之间直接传输,而不通过服务器."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_notice.html.heex:2
